# AI-agent config. The shared .claude/settings.json is committed and
# contains a narrow allow list scoped to read-only shell commands. The
# .claude/settings.local.json sibling is per-developer and MUST NOT be
# committed — it can carry broad Bash(…) grants that would land in
# every clone.
.claude/settings.local.json
